title: 11/03/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/03/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to Peter King about why Deshaun Watson or Odell Beckham Jr. weren't moved at the deadline. NFL Network's Tom Pelissero checks in about the possibility of the Broncos loading up for Aaron Rodgers. Cincinnati Bearcats Head Coach Luke Fickell shares his reaction to being ranked 6th in the first CFP Ranking. And Andy Staples tells us what surprised him most about the rankings.
